## 📊 5. Latency & Safety Guarantees
| Constraint | Implementation | Verification |
|------------|----------------|--------------|
| **p95 first-token ≤ 500ms** | Pre-LLM cost check uses Redis cache + O(1) heuristic. Heavy scoring runs `@Async` post-stream. | Micrometer histogram `aria.cost_check_ms` p95 ≤ 8ms |
| **Zero cross-LOB leakage** | App-layer `lob_code` filter on all cost queries. JWT claims validated pre-interceptor. | Integration test: LOB_A user cannot query LOB_B cost metrics |
| **PII safety** | Cost interceptor never logs prompt/response text. Only token counts, model IDs, and hashes. | Red team test: PII in prompt → cost metric contains zero PII strings |
| **Developer access** | Schema uses `ALTER TABLE` + standard indexes. No `DBMS_RLS`, no partitioning dependencies. | `user_tables` + `user_indexes` validation script passes |

